                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 4992/13.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Fletcher</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Peking</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1907-10-09">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 9, 1907</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Fletcher reports that the Chinese authorities at Mukden have been instructed
                    to surrender McKinley. He requests instructions by telegraph as to custody.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
